{"tid":1740613,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"革命搞到民不聊生 真係第一次見","createTime":"2019-11-20T03:57:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T07:35:26.000Z","uid":338253,"like":23,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"24420a65ed031bb9d927d19e5469d6077b21fc13","tid":1740613,"uid":338253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T03:57:05.000Z","msg":"從來只有<span style=\"color: orange;\">民不聊生</span>生<span style=\"color: red;\">革命</span>，沒有<span style=\"color: red;\">革命</span>生<span style=\"color: orange;\">民不聊生</span><br />\n<br />\n5個月黎反送中運動對整個香港經濟影響好少<br />\n就算你爆360都好 360都只係一間中小企<br />\n香港核心既<span style=\"color: red;\">經濟命脈</span> 大家完全未觸及到<br />\n香港股市 樓市共無太大影響 就如活在<span style=\"color: red;\">平衡時空</span><br />\n但諗深一層 會唔會其實係我地活在平衡時空？5個月啦大哥<br />\n香港反送中活動和香港經濟正在<span style=\"color: red;\">個別發展</span><br />\n最奇特係等人權法通過 但現在通過了 作用真係唔大<br />\n<br />\n其實大家都知道如何<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">攬炒香港經濟</span></span> 只係大家唔敢做<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">大家都為自己，自私，不敢令香港完全停罷</span>"},{"pid":"f9b6f36967465ed0a6ad7e90fab1e6f0892cf79e","tid":1740613,"uid":24814,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T04:00:06.000Z","msg":"公會大罷工<br />\n世上未有一個地方能夠全城自行罷工<br />\n<br />\n簡單啲 剪中環網線 放炸彈"},{"pid":"2f422e73ac45bc401f6f0eeb3df71559f0a3f625","tid":1740613,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T04:00:43.000Z","msg":"咁係點做"},{"pid":"6d1f9c27430e7de79caee5cd8839ddea395281e9","tid":1740613,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T04:02:47.000Z","msg":"某程度你logic都好岩"},{"pid":"a3a24d8b1f51169e0e40dc3d40516a09c5376f77","tid":1740613,"uid":159448,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T04:05:22.000Z","msg":"最驚攬炒既係連登仔"},{"pid":"72d132b3001c78e2957762e9915d351943608d17","tid":1740613,"uid":169195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T04:05:25.000Z","msg":"古時就係無飯開個班革命<br />\n但係人類生活質素提升 而家開倒飯都